</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Eds: EZZARD COLUMN and YOUNG-COLUMN will not move this week.
 &HT;    
 &HT;    CoxNet Cox News Service budget
 &HT;    FOR MONDAY, April 10, 2000
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   For questions, please call 404-526-5456.
