<P>
   IRS ENFORCEMENT FALLS IN 'REFORM' ERA
</P>
<P>
   Seizures of property:
</P>
<P>
   1998: 2,300
</P>
<P>
   1999: 161
</P>
<P>
   Levies of bank accounts, salaries
</P>
<P>
   1998: 2.5 million
</P>
<P>
   1999: 0.5 million
</P>
<P>
   Individual returns audited:
</P>
<P>
   1997: 1.28 percent
</P>
<P>
   1998: 0.99 percent
</P>
<P>
   1999: 0.90 percent
</P>
