   BBA-MARINERS (Seattle) _ Mariners vs. Yankees.
</P>
<P>
   By John Hickey. (Story will move in the ``s'' category.)
</P>
<P>
   FOOD-COLUMN-OWEN (Undated) _ As you may have heard or read, some
of the brightest minds on Madison Avenue have been recruited to
help generate more recruits for the Army, Navy, Air Force and
Marines. So far their efforts have achieved minimal results. First
you have to define the problem. And as any veteran can attest, the
pay is bad, the hours are lousy, the clothes don't fit and the food
is inedible.
</P>
<P>
   By John Owen. (Story will move in the ``d'' category.)
